<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>WeLuvLax</title>
  <meta name="description" content="WeLuvLax - preppy, feminine lacrosse-inspired apparel and lifestyle brand." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #f59ac2;
      --pink-dark: #d96ca0;
      --brown: #4c362d;
      --cream: #fff8fc;
      --soft: #fde8f1;
      --text: #2e1f28;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(76, 54, 45, 0.10);
      --radius: 22px;
    }* { box-sizing: border-box; }

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  color: var(--text);
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left, #fff0f7 0%, #fff8fc 40%, #ffffff 100%);
  line-height: 1.5;
}

a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit; }

.container {
  width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 32px));
  margin: 0 auto;
}

header {
  position: sticky;
  top: 0;
  z-index: 20;
  backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
  background: rgba(255, 248, 252, 0.84);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(217, 108, 160, 0.15);
}

.nav {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 16px 0;
  gap: 16px;
}

.logo {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  color: var(--brown);
}

.logo span { color: var(--pink-dark); }

.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 22px;
  font-size: 0.98rem;
  color: #5e4752;
}

.cta-btn,
.hero-cta,
.secondary-btn {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 14px 22px;
  font-weight: 700;
  transition: 0.2s ease;
  cursor: pointer;
}

.cta-btn,
.hero-cta {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pink), var(--pink-dark));
  color: var(--white);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.cta-btn:hover,
.hero-cta:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  filter: brightness(1.02);
}

.secondary-btn {
  border: 1px solid rgba(76, 54, 45, 0.16);
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
  color: var(--brown);
}

.secondary-btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  background: var(--white);
}

.hero {
  padding: 72px 0 54px;
}

.hero-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.15fr 0.85fr;
  gap: 28px;
  align-items: center;
}

.eyebrow {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--soft);
  color: var(--pink-dark);
  padding: 8px 14px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 0.86rem;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

h1 {
  margin: 0 0 16px;
  font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  line-height: 0.95;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  color: var(--brown);
}

.hero p {
  margin: 0 0 26px;
  font-size: 1.06rem;
  max-width: 620px;
  color: #624e57;
}

.hero-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: 14px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.hero-note {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: #7b6570;
}

.card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.92);
  border: 1px solid rgba(217, 108, 160, 0.14);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.hero-visual {
  padding: 28px;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero-visual::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  width: 180px;
  height: 180px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(245, 154, 194, 0.18);
  top: -40px;
  right: -40px;
}

.hero-stack {
  position: relative;
  display: grid;
  gap: 16px;
}

.mockup {
  border-radius: 20px;
  padding: 22px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fffafd 0%, #fff0f7 100%);
  border: 1px solid rgba(217, 108, 160, 0.15);
}

.mockup.dark {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, #4b3640 0%, #2e2027 100%);
  color: white;
}

.mini-label {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  opacity: 0.75;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.big-brand {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 900;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.big-brand .pink { color: var(--pink); }
.big-brand .heart { color: var(--pink-dark); }

.tagline {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  opacity: 0.85;
}

.section {
  padding: 22px 0 64px;
}

.section-head {
  display: flex;
  align-items: end;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.section h2 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
  color: var(--brown);
}

.section-copy {
  max-width: 680px;
  color: #6a5760;
}

.products,
.features,
.social-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 18px;
}

.products {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
}

.product-card,
.feature-card,
.social-card {
  padding: 22px;
}

.product-top {
  height: 180px;
  border-radius: 18px;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde9f2, #fffefe);
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(217, 108, 160, 0.14);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--brown);
  text-align: center;
  padding: 14px;
}

.product-card h3,
.feature-card h3,
.social-card h3 {
  margin: 0 0 10px;
  color: var(--brown);
}

.price {
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--pink-dark);
  margin-top: 12px;
}

.features {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
}

.icon {
  width: 48px;
  height: 48px;
  border-radius: 14px;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  background: var(--soft);
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.newsletter {
  padding: 30px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 18px;
  align-items: center;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c362d, #6b4b57);
  color: white;
}

.newsletter h3 {
  margin: 0 0 8px;
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.newsletter-form {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: flex-end;
}

input[type="email"] {
  min-width: 260px;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 999px;
  padding: 14px 18px;
  font-size: 1rem;
  outline: none;
}

button {
  border: none;
  font: inherit;
}

.social-grid {
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
}

footer {
  padding: 28px 0 48px;
  color: #735d66;
}

.footer-row {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(217, 108, 160, 0.15);
  padding-top: 22px;
}

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .hero-grid,
  .newsletter,
  .products,
  .features,
  .social-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: none;
  }

  .newsletter-form {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
}

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <a href="#top" class="logo">We<span>Luv</span>Lax</a>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="#shop">Shop</a>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#community">Community</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <a href="#shop" class="cta-btn">Shop the Drop</a>
    </div>
  </header>  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Preppy. Feminine. Lacrosse.</div>
          <h1>WeLuvLax</h1>
          <p>
            A playful, polished lacrosse lifestyle brand built for girls who love the game,
            the style, and the energy around it. Think elevated hoodies, clean graphics, and a pink-forward identity.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="#shop" class="hero-cta">Shop Coming Soon</a>
            <a href="#about" class="secondary-btn">See the Brand</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-note">Launch collection in progress. Apparel, accessories, and team-spirit staples coming soon.</div>
        </div><div class="card hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-stack">
        <div class="mockup dark">
          <div class="mini-label">Signature mark</div>
          <div class="big-brand">
            We<span class="pink">Luv</span>Lax <span class="heart">♡</span>
          </div>
          <div class="tagline">Pink-forward apparel with a crisp lacrosse attitude.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="mockup">
          <div class="mini-label">Brand feel</div>
          <div class="big-brand" style="font-size:1.8rem; color: var(--brown);">Game day, but make it cute.</div>
          <div class="tagline">Clean, feminine pieces designed for players, fans, and proud lax families.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="shop">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <h2>Featured Pieces</h2>
        <div class="section-copy">Use these as starter product categories until you add real product photos and checkout links.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="products">
      <div class="card product-card">
        <div class="product-top">Signature Hoodie<br/>Pink logo on black</div>
        <h3>Classic WeLuvLax Hoodie</h3>
        <p>Soft everyday staple with the core logo treatment. Clean enough for a left-chest version or bold front print.</p>
        <div class="price">From $48</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card product-card">
        <div class="product-top">Crewneck Sweatshirt<br/>Preppy athletic fit</div>
        <h3>Weekend Crew</h3>
        <p>Simple, polished, and easy to layer. Built for tournament mornings, sidelines, and after-practice comfort.</p>
        <div class="price">From $42</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card product-card">
        <div class="product-top">Accessories & Gifts<br/>Bows, bags, extras</div>
        <h3>Sideline Essentials</h3>
        <p>Accessories that carry the same brand energy: sporty, feminine, giftable, and team-friendly.</p>
        <div class="price">Coming Soon</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <h2>What the Brand Stands For</h2>
        <div class="section-copy">This section gives the site substance even before you launch full ecommerce.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features">
      <div class="card feature-card">
        <div class="icon">♡</div>
        <h3>Feminine Identity</h3>
        <p>Pink-forward visuals, polished layouts, and a brand style that feels sporty without losing its softness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card feature-card">
        <div class="icon">🥍</div>
        <h3>Lacrosse First</h3>
        <p>Built around real lacrosse culture, not generic athleticwear. This is for people who actually live the sport.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card feature-card">
        <div class="icon">✦</div>
        <h3>Preppy Edge</h3>
        <p>Clean branding, easy layering, and a refined look that works on campus, at tournaments, and everywhere in between.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card newsletter">
      <div>
        <h3>Be first for the launch</h3>
        <p>Collect emails now, even before the store is fully live. Replace this form action later with Shopify, Mailchimp, or another email platform.</p>
      </div>
      <form class="newsletter-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Thanks! You can connect this form later to your email platform.');">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
        <button class="cta-btn" type="submit">Join the List</button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="community">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head">
      <div>
        <h2>Community Energy</h2>
        <div class="section-copy">Placeholder content that makes the brand feel active right away.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="social-grid">
      <div class="card social-card">
        <h3>Tournament Days</h3>
        <p>Style content, warmups, and sideline fits that turn game-day energy into brand identity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card social-card">
        <h3>Team Spirit</h3>
        <p>Future space for school colors, team collections, or special drops built around programs and events.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card social-card">
        <h3>Giftable Gear</h3>
        <p>Perfect for players, parents, and supporters looking for a more elevated lacrosse gift option.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  </main>  <footer id="contact">
    <div class="container footer-row">
      <div><strong>WeLuvLax</strong> — Lacrosse lifestyle apparel with a feminine, preppy feel.</div>
      <div>Instagram: @weluvlax &nbsp;|&nbsp; Email: hello@weluvlax.com</div>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
